---
// Process component showing our methodology
---

<section id="process" class="process section-animate">
  <div class="section-container">
    <h2>Our Method</h2>
    <p class="section-description">We follow a proven methodology to ensure successful outcomes for every project.</p>
    
    <div class="process-grid">
      <div class="step card-animate">
        <div class="icon-placeholder">1</div>
        <h3>Discovery</h3>
        <p>We begin by understanding your vision, goals, and the challenges you face.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="step card-animate">
        <div class="icon-placeholder">2</div>
        <h3>Strategy</h3>
        <p>We develop a comprehensive plan that aligns with your objectives and timeline.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="step card-animate">
        <div class="icon-placeholder">3</div>
        <h3>Execution</h3>
        <p>We implement the strategy with precision, keeping you informed every step of the way.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="step card-animate">
        <div class="icon-placeholder">4</div>
        <h3>Results</h3>
        <p>We measure success and ensure your goals are achieved, then plan for future growth.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .process {
    background-color: #F8F9FA;
  }

  .section-description {
    font-size: 1.575rem; /* 5% larger: 1.5rem to 1.575rem */
    color: var(--text-dark);
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 5.25rem; /* 5% larger: 5rem to 5.25rem */
    max-width: 840px; /* 5% larger: 800px to 840px */
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .process-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(315px, 1fr)); /* 5% larger: 300px to 315px */
    gap: 3.15rem; /* 5% larger: 3rem to 3.15rem */
    margin-top: 4.2rem; /* 5% larger: 4rem to 4.2rem */
    justify-items: start;
  }

  .step {
    text-align: left;
    padding: 3.15rem; /* 5% larger: 3rem to 3.15rem */
    background-color: white;
    border-radius: 12.6px; /* 5% larger: 12px to 12.6px */
    box-shadow: 0 6.3px 31.5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* 5% larger shadows */
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    min-height: 315px; /* 5% larger: 300px to 315px */
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-start;
  }

  .step:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8.4px); /* 5% larger: -8px to -8.4px */
    box-shadow: 0 12.6px 42px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15); /* 5% larger shadows */
  }

  .icon-placeholder {
    width: 84px; /* 5% larger: 80px to 84px */
    height: 84px; /* 5% larger: 80px to 84px */
    background: var(--accent-blue);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 2.1rem; /* 5% larger: 2rem to 2.1rem */
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2.1rem; /* 5% larger: 2rem to 2.1rem */
  }

  .step h3 {
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 1.575rem; /* 5% larger: 1.5rem to 1.575rem */
  }

  .step p {
    text-align: left;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.155rem; /* 5% larger: 1.1rem to 1.155rem */
  }

  @media (min-width: 1920px) {
    .process-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(420px, 1fr)); /* 5% larger: 400px to 420px */
      gap: 4.2rem; /* 5% larger: 4rem to 4.2rem */
    }

    .step {
      padding: 4.2rem; /* 5% larger: 4rem to 4.2rem */
      min-height: 367.5px; /* 5% larger: 350px to 367.5px */
    }

    .icon-placeholder {
      width: 105px; /* 5% larger: 100px to 105px */
      height: 105px; /* 5% larger: 100px to 105px */
      font-size: 2.625rem; /* 5% larger: 2.5rem to 2.625rem */
    }

    .section-description {
      font-size: 1.8375rem; /* 5% larger: 1.75rem to 1.8375rem */
      margin-bottom: 6.3rem; /* 5% larger: 6rem to 6.3rem */
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-description {
      font-size: 1.155rem; /* 5% larger: 1.1rem to 1.155rem */
      margin-bottom: 3.15rem; /* 5% larger: 3rem to 3.15rem */
    }

    .process-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.1rem; /* 5% larger: 2rem to 2.1rem */
    }

    .step {
      padding: 1.575rem; /* 5% larger: 1.5rem to 1.575rem */
      min-height: auto;
    }

    .icon-placeholder {
      width: 47.25px; /* 5% larger: 45px to 47.25px */
      height: 47.25px; /* 5% larger: 45px to 47.25px */
      font-size: 1.155rem; /* 5% larger: 1.1rem to 1.155rem */
      margin-bottom: 1.05rem; /* 5% larger: 1rem to 1.05rem */
    }
  }
</style>
